name: UINotificationFeedbackGenerator.FeedbackType
desc: The type of notification generated by a UINotificationFeedbackGenerator object.

items.name: case error
items.desc: A notification feedback type, indicating that a task has failed.

items.name: case success
items.desc: A notification feedback type, indicating that a task has completed successfully.

items.name: case warning
items.desc: A notification feedback type, indicating that a task has produced a warning.
